FBIS3-15889 "drsov048_m_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-048 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Mar 1994 Tajikistan Deputy Prime Minister Assassinated at Home LD1103060594 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0545 GMT 11 Mar 94 LD1103060594 Moscow ITAR-TASS Language: English Article Type:BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Galina Gridneva] [Text] Dushanbe March 11 TASS -- Tajikistan's Vice-Premier Mayonsho Nazarshoyev was shot and killed in his apartment in the early hours on Friday. Unidentified assassins were armed with an automatic gun, a source on the information department of the Tajik Ministry of Foreign Affairs told ITAR-TASS. The sources promised more information later.
